es.com/1995-01-06/entertainment/ca-17089_1_vocal-performance/1|title=The 37th Grammy Nominations|date=January 6, 1995|accessdate=July 12, 2010|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=Tribune Company|page=1}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" align=\"center\"|[[Grammy Awards of 1996|1996]]\n| {{sortname|Seal||Seal (musician)}}<br />{{small|{{dot}}produced by [[Trevor Horn]]}}\n| {{sort|Kiss from a Rose|\"[[Kiss from a Rose]]\"}} *\n|\n* {{small|\"[[One Sweet Day]]\" by [[Mariah Carey]] & [[Boyz II Men]]}}\n* {{small|\"[[Gangsta's Paradise (song)|Gangsta's Paradise]]\" by [[Coolio]]}}\n* {{small|\"[[One of Us (Joan Osborne song)|One of Us]]\" by [[Joan Osborne]]}}\n* {{small|\"[[Waterfalls (TLC song)|Waterfalls]]\" by [[TLC (band)|TLC]]}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=Grammy1996>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/Music/9601/grammy_noms/grammy_list.html|title=List of Grammy nominees|date=January 4, 1996|accessdate=July 12, 2010|publisher=CNN}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" align=\"center\"|[[Grammy Awards of 1997|1997]]\n| {{sortname|Eric|Clapton}}<br />{{small|{{dot}}produced by [[Kenneth \"Babyface\" Edmonds|Babyface]]}}\n| {{sort|Change the World|\"[[Change the World]]\"}} *\n|\n* {{small|\"[[Give Me One Reason]]\" by [[Tracy Chapman]]}}\n* {{small|\"[[Because You Loved Me]]\" by [[Celine Dion]]}}\n* {{small|\"[[Ironic (song)|Ironic]]\" by [[Alanis Morissette]]}}\n* {{small|\"[[1979 (song)|1979]]\" by [[The Smashing Pumpkins]]}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=Grammy1997>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HKQaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Ci4EAAAAIBAJ&pg=4773,8816303&dq|title=Babyface is up for 12 Grammy awards|date=January 8, 1997|accessdate=July 12, 2010|work=[[Milwaukee Journal Sentinel]]|first=Mary|last=Campbell}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===1990s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#bebebe\"\n! width=\"5%\" | Year\n! width=\"20%\" | Record\n! width=\"20%\" | Artist(s)\n! width=\"55%\" | Production team\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" style