 Dave Fortman]]\n[[Category:Alternative metal albums by American artists]]\n[[Category:Epic Records albums]]\n[[Category:Evanescence albums]]\n[[Category:Wind-up Records albums]]\n", "name_user": "SnapSnap", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eCertifications", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fallen_(Evanescence_album)"}
