alls |first1=Noreen |last2=Levitt |first2=Alexandra |last3=Kanade |first3=Neha |last4=Wright-Jegede |first4=Narue |last5=Dopson |first5=Stephanie |last6=Biggerstaff |first6=Matthew |last7=Reed |first7=Carrie |last8=Uzicanin |first8=Amra |last9=Levitt |first9=Alexandra |last10=Dopson |first10=Stephanie |last11=Frank |first11=Mark |last12=Holloway |first12=Rachel |last13=Koonin |first13=Lisa |last14=Rasmussen |first14=Sonja |last15=Redd |first15=Stephen |last16=de la Motte Hurst |first16=Christopher |last17=Kanade |first17=Neha |last18=Qualls |first18=Noreen |last19=Rainey |first19=Jeanette |last20=Uzicanin |first20=Amra |last21=Biggerstaff |first21=Matthew |last22=Jernigan |first22=Daniel |last23=Reed |first23=Carrie |title=Community Mitigation Guidelines to Prevent Pandemic Influenza\u2014United States, 2017 |journal=MMWR. Recommendations and Reports |date=21 April 2017 |volume=66 |issue=1 |pages=1\u201334 |doi=10.15585/mmwr.rr6601a1 |pmid=28426646 |pmc=5837128}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NY0JD\">{{cite web |url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/what-it-means-to-contain-and-mitigate-the-coronavirus |title=What It Means to Contain and Mitigate the Coronavirus |first=Robert P. |last=Baird |date=11 March 2020 |work=[[The New Yorker]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RwmYm\">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/07/world/asia/china-coronavirus-cost.html |title=China May Be Beating the Coronavirus, at a Painful Cost |first=Amy |last=Qin |work=[[The New York Times]] |date=7 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"shZdf\">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/11/mass-testing-alerts-and-big-fines-the-strategies-used-in-asia-to-slow-coronavirus |title=Mass testing, alerts and big fines: the strategies used in Asia to slow coronavirus |first1=Justin McCurry Rebecca Ratcliffe in |last1=Bangkok |first2=Helen Davidson in Hong |last2=Kong |date=11 March 2020 |work=[[The Guardian]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"hxm4a\">{{cite web |url=https://www.ebmedicine.net/topics/i